<t anchor="source-asciirfc-header-mauthors-v3" keepWithNext="true">EXAMPLE  4: AsciiRFC Document Header With Multiple Authors (RFC XML v3)</t><sourcecode anchor="_ef14e98f-0dc3-424b-89ef-96676d3c9156" type="xml"><![CDATA[<CODE BEGINS>
Unresolved directive in sections/04-header.adoc - include::../examples/rfc-divination-cfapi/xml3/draft-divination-cfapi.xml[lines=11..47]
